             was indicted for <rs id="t17870711-2-off7" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17870711-2-off7" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17870711-2-off7" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17870711-2-cd8" type="crimeDate">9th day of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870711-2-off7 t17870711-2-cd8"></join> last, one silver watch, value 30 s. a steel chain, value 6 d. a seal, value 2 d. a key value 2 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17870711-2-victim70" type="victimName">
                  Richard 
                  Hale
               <interp inst="t17870711-2-victim70" type="surname" value="Hale"></interp>
